preference.name: TC_external_Requirements_proxy_props_external
preference.preference_description: Defines the properties of each proxy object imported from Teamcenter systems engineering and requirements management to be stored in Teamcenter. Valid Values: Any valid Teamcenter property names of workspace objects. Properties specified in this preference must correlate exactly to the properties specified in the TC_external_Requirements_proxy_props_internal site preference.
